<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Damsung tuilien ah thikdet na tu nam?
 Meipi hung zina, lungkhamna hung let tieng;
 Tui kinawk san a, a hun sukbuoi tieng,
 Na thikdet a tawkmang em, a det zing nam?

[V2]
 Thagau vawp bit thei, thikdet I nei,
 Tui hung let lai ale muonum zing;
 Tawilawk ngeilo Suongpi chuh belin,
 Hukdampa hehpihna a kinga chuh.

[V3]
 2. Tuihat lauhum ah thikdet na tu nam?
 Tui a hung let a lauhum a hung naih tieng;
 Tui a kinawka, huih hat a nun tieng,
 Tuilien bang cheng hung mahleh na bit zing na'm?

[V4]
 3. Thihna tui sanglien ah thikdet na tu'm,
 Tuilien in a hun chup a, thih a naih tieng?
 Tui kinawk lak achun tum ngei puon la,
 Muonuma na thikdet a kingak zing chun.

[V5]
 4. Zing khawvak ah na mitin a mu dem?
 Sana khawpi leh kuong chawlhna mun vak chu?
 Luipang ah na thikdet a bit na dem?
 Damsung tuilien kum khuo'n a beihmang tieng leh.</lyrics>
<title>WILLYOUR ANCHOR HOLD?</title>
</song>